{"type":"answer","id":117365,"parentType":"question","parentId":14338,"uid":13737,"contents":"<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/bJzTOeWm.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bJzTOeWm.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/bJzTOeWm.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n我们贵州省旗。<br>\n<br>\n底部是三色横条，分别代表白苗、青苗、黑苗，宽度大致反映人口比例。<br>\n<br>\n中央是橙色苗寨徽标。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n苗族是我们贵州的原住民。今天的贵州汉人，主体也是明代以后分批汉化的苗人。所以我省必定要以苗文化为主。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n将来有空再设计反映侗文化的玉屏县旗。","date":"2019-12-30","agreeCount":3,"discussionCount":0}